targets.query: SELECT last("target") - (last("target") * $CpuLoadAcceptVarInt / 10000 / 100.0) FROM "cs_agent_cpu", "$EventTable" WHERE "session" =~ /^$SessionId$/ AND "ip_address" =~ /^$IpAddress$/ AND $timeFilter

SELECT last("ops_target_read_rate") - (last("ops_target_read_rate") * $MemReadRateAcceptVarInt / 10000 / 100.0) FROM "cs_agent_memory", "$EventTable" WHERE "session" =~ /^$SessionId$/ AND "ip_address" =~ /^$IpAddress$/ AND $timeFilter

SELECT last("ops_target_write_rate") - (last("ops_target_write_rate") * $MemWriteRateAcceptVarInt / 10000 / 100.0) FROM "cs_agent_memory", "$EventTable" WHERE "session" =~ /^$SessionId$/ AND "ip_address" =~ /^$IpAddress$/ AND $timeFilter

SELECT last("ops_target_read_rate") - (last("ops_target_read_rate") * $NetReadRateAcceptVarInt / 10000 / 100.0) FROM "cs_agent_network", "$EventTable" WHERE "session" =~ /^$SessionId$/ AND "ip_address" =~ /^$IpAddress$/ AND $timeFilter

SELECT last("ops_target_write_rate") - (last("ops_target_write_rate") * $MemWriteRateAcceptVarInt / 10000 / 100.0) FROM "cs_agent_network", "$EventTable" WHERE "session" =~ /^$SessionId$/ AND "ip_address" =~ /^$IpAddress$/ AND $timeFilter

SELECT last("ops_target_read_rate") - (last("ops_target_read_rate") * $StorReadRateAcceptVarInt / 10000 / 100.0) FROM "cs_agent_block", "$EventTable" WHERE "session" =~ /^$SessionId$/ AND "ip_address" =~ /^$IpAddress$/ AND $timeFilter

SELECT last("ops_target_write_rate") - (last("ops_target_write_rate") * $StorReadRateAcceptVarInt / 10000 / 100.0) FROM "cs_agent_block", "$EventTable" WHERE "session" =~ /^$SessionId$/ AND "ip_address" =~ /^$IpAddress$/ AND $timeFilter
